description:
Friends, time is short. If this was our last year, what would you do differently? Would you pray and read your Bible more? Would you witness more or give more generously to God's work? Or is there someone you need to reconcile with? Whatever it may be, do it now! Let's live with eternity in mind.

If you would like to make a donation, here is the link! www.bit.ly/3uRYNmz
